About Us
MARSA (Maron Space Agency) is a Ugandan-based applied physics and innovation group focused on advancing science, technology, and space research. Our mission is to inspire innovation and build solutions that empower Africa and beyond.
Our Projects
Applied Physics Lab
Hands-on experiments and prototypes in energy, mechanics, and material science.
Space Research
Exploring possibilities of satellite technology, astronomy, and space exploration.
STEM Education
Sharing knowledge through workshops, mentoring, and online resources for young scientists.
